  "title": "Pre-school English Teacher",
  "description": "<p>Job Descriptions:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for planning &amp; implementing program for preschool.</li>\n  <li>Execute teaching, learning, and nurturing activities suitable for children's development, in line with applicable curriculum guidelines.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to health, safety, nutritional, and hygiene standards and procedures.</li>\n  <li>Maintain the accurate records of children's progress and growth.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with parents on child’s development and address their concerns appropriately.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with other teachers ongoing projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess L2 Certificate</li>\n  <li>Friendly and good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Candidate with minimum 2 years of similar job scope experience</li>\n  <li>PC literate</li>\n  <li>Team player with strong communication skills</li>\n  <li>Workplace to be at 1079 Serangoon Road.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want to be part of a great team to build up the leading holistic preschool band, apply today. We offer competitive remunerations. Interested candidates please send the followings to: <a href=\"mailto:hr@charis.sg\">hr@charis.sg</a></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Resume</li>\n  <li>Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving previous and current employment</li>\n  <li>Notice period</li>\n</ul>",
